[I] A GTK+ based programmers editor remotely similar to UltraEdit-32

[T] A text editor that is intended to be lightweight, but full of useful
[T] features for programming, from websites editing to C coding. Supports
[T] many languages through config files and offers functions such as
[T] syntax highlighting, automatic indentation, completion and correction.

[U] https://www.nongnu.org/beaver/

